{"tid":1724232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警屯門拘兩外籍青年　涉非法集結違《禁蒙面法》 (19:30)","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T14:39:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":148,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"795518e8600308fd87cbcb542db161c5128ef84c","tid":1724232,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:58:10.000Z","msg":"【19:30】據了解，兩名被捕男子均為嶺南大學交換生。<br />\n<br />\n【17:28】反修例風波下各區有多人示威抗議，昨晚（14日）一批示威者在屯門鄉事會路與杯渡路交界聚集，警方到場展開驅散行動，並在屯匯街一巴士站截查兩名分別22及23歲外籍男子。<br />\n<br />\n經調查後，該名22歲外籍男子涉非法集結及違反《禁止蒙面規例》被捕，另一23歲外籍男子涉嫌非法集結被捕。二人正被扣留調查，案件交由屯門警區重案組人員跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191115/s00001/1573809090933/%e8%ad%a6%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e6%8b%98%e5%85%a9%e5%a4%96%e7%b1%8d%e9%9d%92%e5%b9%b4-%e6%b6%89%e9%9d%9e%e6%b3%95%e9%9b%86%e7%b5%90%e9%81%95%e3%80%8a%e7%a6%81%e8%92%99%e9%9d%a2%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191115%2Fs00001%2F1573809090933%2F%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e6%258b%2598%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25a4%2596%25e7%25b1%258d%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b9%25b4-%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%259d%259e%25e6%25b3%2595%25e9%259b%2586%25e7%25b5%2590%25e9%2581%2595%25e3%2580%258a%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%258b&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=550d52e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191115%2Fs00001%2F1573809090933%2F%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e6%258b%2598%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25a4%2596%25e7%25b1%258d%25e9%259d%2592%25e5%25b9%25b4-%25e6%25b6%2589%25e9%259d%259e%25e6%25b3%2595%25e9%259b%2586%25e7%25b5%2590%25e9%2581%2595%25e3%2580%258a%25e7%25a6%2581%25e8%2592%2599%25e9%259d%25a2%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3